Controversial cross-dresser, Bobrisky, on Wednesday, gifted disqualified Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, Erica one million naira. Bobrisky disclosed this on her Instagram page. She shared a screenshot of Erica confirming the money. The controversial cross-dresser made the promise to gift Erica one million naira after she got disqualified from BBNaija Lockdown house. Recall that Erica was disqualified after she received a strike for flouting major house rules. Her disqualification got Nigerian celebrities making promises to help her outside the house. Some fans even went ahead to open a Gofundme account, which stirred reactions from some Nigerians on social media.<img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-840408" src="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/unnamed-4.jpg" alt="" width="748" height="731" srcset="https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/unnamed-4.jpg 748w, https://dailypost.ng/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/unnamed-4-300x293.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px">